Step 1: Start
Step 2: Enter Bucket Size, Number of Incoming Packets and Outgoing Rate
Step 3: Initialize Store to 0
Step 4: Repeat steps 5 to 13 for Number of Incoming Packets
Step 5: Enter Incoming Size
Step 6: If Incoming Size less than Bucket Size - Store, go to step 7. Else go to step 9
Step 7: Add Incoming to Store
Step 8: Print Store and Bucket Size. Go to Step 12
Step 9: Print Dropped Packets
Step 10: Print Store and Bucket Size
Step 11: Set Store as Bucket Size
Step 12: Set Store as Store - Outgoing
Step 13: Print Store and Bucket Size after Outgoing
Step 14: Stop